5. UPDATES AND TELEMETRY

The Software includes an automatic update mechanism. It periodically checks
for updates by requesting manifest files from Swim Code's release server;
these requests carry no personal data and no usage telemetry. Updates are
never downloaded or installed without your explicit action, and automatic
update checks can be disabled in Settings.

The Software contains no analytics, crash reporting, or usage tracking.
Information about how you use the Software is not transmitted to Swim Code.
Handling of account authentication and any data transmitted to third-party
AI providers, source control services, or other integrations you configure
is governed by the Privacy Policy.

